{"tid":231881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盼成職業選手電競少女　棄考DSE追夢","createTime":"2017-05-06T11:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T13:12:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c91a8fe9b3efec7d22f1f102d51b66dd14a08075","tid":231881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20012570&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170506\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20012570%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170506&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1dadbf12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20012570%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170506&h=7b94efa3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20012570&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170506</a><br />\n<br />\n盼成職業選手<br />\n電競少女　棄考DSE追夢<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為夢想，你可以去到幾盡？為入大學，中學生在文憑試（DSE）爭個頭崩額裂，惟兩名應屆考生，為成為職業電競選手，毅然放棄學業。17歲的彭泳熙，成績一直不俗，老師更預測她物理和數學延伸部份可奪5*佳績，但她全部科目考試都缺席，就是為了追夢。<br />\n記者：李詠希<br />\n<br />\n泳熙自中四暑假開始打機，中五立志將來要成為職業電競選手，現為電競女子隊Miss Ripper的成員。她說因打機成績下滑，老師不斷用DSE向她「洗腦」，反而令她驚醒，「之前以為讀書係為求知識，但原來只係為咗DSE」，故不想隨波逐流爭入大學。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n彭泳熙自中四暑假開始打機，中五時就立志成為職業電競選手。<br />\n朱永倫攝<br />\n<br />\n女王盃亞軍拒考大學<br />\n<br />\n一心爭飲香港電競業的「頭啖湯」的泳熙說：「老師都有問點解唔考埋DSE先追夢，但𠵱家香港電競起步，需要有人支持，如果做第二、第三批嘅話就會太遲。」她指，電競要靠個人實力，更不是賺不到錢，現時開始開台直播打機，已陸續有觀眾捐款，期望盡快儲更多人氣和提升實力，令自己無悔。<br />\n另一電競女子隊Team Dream Force成員、19歲的鄧惋心，DSE期間仍參加「英雄聯盟女王盃」，奪得亞軍，她當時要每周團練4至5日，有時更練習至凌晨2時，因此放棄考入大學。<br />\n「一生人讀咁多書就係為DSE，自己都覺得對屋企人唔住」。自言性格「3分鐘熱度」的惋心，不輕言放棄自己夢想，更為此與家人鬧翻，游說多次，父母態度稍為軟化，「家人話畀一年時間我，如果冇成績或者要解散，我就要走，搵份穩定嘅工」。<br />\n惋心近年打過4至5場比賽，除了自身努力，也期望政府制訂相關政策扶助香港電競業發展。她指出，香港目前缺乏正規課程培訓電競人才，又指與其政府投資搞大型電競活動，倒不如花錢進行更多貼地宣傳，如介紹電競業的出路等。<br />\n泳熙也同意此說法，批評政府欠缺對電競的宣傳，令年輕人不敢入行。她指，香港不乏有實力的電競選手，但缺乏扶助，就會轉到其他事業發展，「咁只會惡性循環落去，一直發展唔到電競」。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n鄧惋心於DSE期間參加「英雄聯盟女王盃」奪得亞軍，決定放棄考大學。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n業界促政府辦正規課程<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;13小時前"},{"pid":"13600b6d2fca63a41073285318ed171d3d0053fe","tid":231881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"彭泳熙自中四暑假開始打機，中五時就立志成為職業電競選手。<br />\n朱永倫攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170506/large/06la8p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170506%2Flarge%2F06la8p1.jpg&h=d0389976&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8803e8066e5ef82fb306f381604b55430e58c5f","tid":231881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"鄧惋心於DSE期間參加「英雄聯盟女王盃」奪得亞軍，決定放棄考大學。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20012570&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170506\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20012570%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170506&h=849cf6e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57493f2df544e5759a6ef7112f0457aeb5387526","tid":231881,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"我養你"},{"pid":"90ff18e35c93b7b28c497566be3db1d20f6ef786","tid":231881,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed3c401358f6c8b8ff86237a2579c177a3c39d02","tid":231881,"uid":57409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年後佢就會後悔</blockquote><br />\n等包養"},{"pid":"271e9040632859d503747b303b51ccc9e57c4fa8","tid":231881,"uid":9729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年後佢就會後悔</blockquote><br />\n好多人練定等亞運架咁快篤爆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b6423d38d84628663af3b68e982a072696bfa3","tid":231881,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"藉口 比啲心0雞湯呃撚哂"},{"pid":"174de8d68419a89c9f90a2da2b3d408efb54ce69","tid":231881,"uid":12831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"佢真係好勁 打sup比mk仔carry都仲係白金（上季鑽）<br />\n咁都打到職業開台...如果你睇緊我想同你講 d人睇你唔係實力 係睇下女咋 實力？鑽石都未有 淨係識sup點打職業"},{"pid":"a1a508664359fdff1c7a0e9895d9e4c81015749c","tid":231881,"uid":57692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T12:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢真係好勁 打sup比mk仔carry都仲係白金（上季鑽）<br />\n咁都打到職業開台...如果你睇緊我想同你講 d人睇你唔係實力 係睇下女咋 實力？鑽石都未有 淨係識sup點打職業</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c3125f168a70b8646b9e78611fa7fbdc2af6fb","tid":231881,"uid":41655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=671549683033568&amp;id=646963552158848&amp;notif_t=like&amp;notif_id=1494074568693463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D671549683033568%26id%3D646963552158848%26notif_t%3Dlike%26notif_id%3D1494074568693463&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7a41262b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=671549683033568&amp;id=646963552158848&amp;notif_t=like&amp;notif_id=1494074568693463</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae188ceff14e8cf418c262c2dfbf61fccefb995","tid":231881,"uid":12831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s